OBJECT

ControllerLayout

A Stone Controller Layout. Describes the layout of a known controller by a collection of element definition.

link GraphQL Schema definition

  • type ControllerLayout implements Node {
  • # The Stone ID of the Controller Layout.
  • controllerId: ControllerId!
  • # The human-readable friendly name of this layout.
  • friendlyName: String!
  • id: ID!
  • # The layout definition of the controller.
  • layout: ControllerElementCollection!
  • # The list of platforms that supports this controller, represented as Stone
  • # Platform IDs.
  • platforms: [PlatformId!]!
  • }

link Require by

  • EmulatedControllerAn association of a real input device to a virtual emulated device being used for an emulation instance.
  • StoneQueryProvides access to Stone platform and controller definitions.
